Authors: Ronak Mehta & Jesse Hoosemans

Visual Human-Readable Form: Defines criteria for lead conversion trigger with the following options:
[Required]
- Criteria: Field update (Select which fields to look at and what values they should have)
- Create Opportunity or not (could be conditional)
- What to do when multiple matching Accounts or Contacts found?
- What Lead Status to set the lead to after conversion
- Run schedule: Instantaneous, Hourly, Daily
- Error Handling: Notify user

[Optional]
- Set Account Owner to someone other than Lead Owner 
- What Account and Contact Record Types to select
- Create Rucurring Gift
- Create <Custom Object> records
